                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#2r">Fol. 2r</locus>: Note on the number of books in the monastic library followed by a hymn praising the Virgin Mary.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           37 books were in the library of the monastery at the time when the note was written.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#182va">Fol. 182va</locus>: Rhymed ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 182va: ዝንቱ፡ ወንጌል፡ ዘጽርሐ፡ ቅድሳት፤ ከመ፡ ይዝክርዋ፡ በጊዜ፡ ጸሎት፡ አማኅፀንኩክሙ፡ ትቤ፡ ለማኅበር፡ ዘደብረ፡ ገነት፡ ወለወልዳ፡ ተርቢኖስ። ወለአቡሃ፡ ዘመለኮት፡ ወለእማ፡ አርአያ፡ ኅሪት፨</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 182va: This Gospel (book belongs) to the chamber of sacred things. That they remember it in the time of prayer, I supplicate you; you say to the community of Däbrä Gännät, and its son Tärbinos, and its father Zä-Mäläkot, and its mother ʾArʾaya Ḫǝrit (?).</q>
                           Written in the main hand.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#182vb">Fols. 182vb-183</locus>ra: Extensive note, for the most part erased.<q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The greater part of the text (fol. 182vb) has been erased, although some letters are still visible. The legible paqssage contains the condemnation formula.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#183ra">Fol. 183ra</locus>-rb: Donation note concerning land.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 183ra-rb: ዘወሀበት፡ ሐመልማለ፡ ወርቅ፡ ገራኅተ፡ ፃዕዳ፡ ሐመድ፡ ለአበ፡ ነፍሳ፡ ቄስ፡ ወልደ፡ ክርስቶስ፡&lt;...&gt; ተዝካራሂ፡ ግበሩ፡ አመ፡ ፴ሁ፡ ለጥቅምት፡ በጊዜ፡ ቊርባን፡ ኢትርሥዑ፡ ስማ፡ ለዓለም።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Written in the main hand, the beginning is missing. About half of the text has been erased.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                           <locus target="#183rb">Fol. 183rb</locus>: Note on commomoration days of some individuals. <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Written in the main hand. The note lists the dates on which the deceased ʾAkalä Krǝstos, Wäldä Krǝstos, Giyorgis and Ṗawlos are commemorated.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                           <locus target="#183v">Fol. 183v</locus>: Short note on the Gospels and Evangelists. <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Written in the main hand. The final part is unintelligible.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Crude notes: fol. 1r.&#xD;
- Crude note in the upper margin: fol. 3r.&#xD;
- Numerous glosses or corrections written in a different hand, throughout the Ms.</item>
